Drži ovo.

02:00:40.006 --> 02:00:41.659
Sranje!

02:00:56.725 --> 02:00:58.355
Kreni!

02:01:36.464 --> 02:01:38.153
Sranje!

02:01:50.640 --> 02:01:52.242
Izlazi vani!

