02:07:07.799 --> 02:07:09.834
Skreni prema rampi!

02:07:19.595 --> 02:07:21.158
Sranje!

02:07:24.226 --> 02:07:25.825
Držite se!

02:08:11.116 --> 02:08:12.714
Nemoj stati!

02:08:20.475 --> 02:08:21.998
Idi ravno!

02:08:24.255 --> 02:08:25.759
Pazi!

02:08:40.423 --> 02:08:42.838
Bježite odavde!

02:08:48.033 --> 02:08:51.298
Idemo odavde! Idemo! Hajde! Idemo!

